name: Impact-displays
overview:
Impact Displays has been a leader in portable trade show displays and modular trade show booths and trade show graphics for more than 15 years. We can help make your next trade show a success – call us! Whether you’re a first time exhibitor or a seasoned pro, trade shows and other face to face marketing events are stressful. Your company’s most valuable assets are presented to thousands of people for a limited engagement performance. You have a lot to worry about – from flight and delivery schedules, meetings, etc. Let us take one issue – getting a great display – off your list of worries.

Call us and let’s work on a trade show display together. We’ll help you be more successful at your next trade show.
